Package: simpson
Type: Package
Title: The Simpson Paradox
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Simon Herrmann
Maintainer: Simon Herrmann <simon.herrmann@campus.lmu.de>
Description: With the help of this package you can learn more about the    
    Simpson Paradox. This package provides sample data and some functions
    that help you explore this statistical phenomenon. Start your learning
    journey with the function hello_simpson().
